      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sample size and repeatability of experimental measurements documented; statistical power analysis not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark dataset includes triplicate measurements at each operating point. Statistical power analysis not required at MRL 2; documented sample adequacy accepted."
    },
