    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out as not required at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 1. The CFD model of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions in support of Class II CPB device regulatory submission. Decision applies to the operating envelope and QoIs described in the Claim and Requirement bindings.",
